sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as API Endpoint
    participant DB as Database
    participant Email as Email Service
    participant Cookie as Cookie Store

    Note over Client,Cookie: Authentication Flow
    Client->>API: GET /api/auth/check
    API->>Cookie: Check admin cookie
    Cookie-->>API: Cookie value
    API->>DB: Query session (optional)
    API-->>Client: { isAuthenticated: true/false }

    Note over Client,Email: Contact Form Flow
    Client->>API: POST /api/contact<br/>{name, email, message}
    API->>API: Validate required fields
    alt Missing fields
        API-->>Client: 400 Bad Request
    else Valid request
        API->>Email: Send email via Gmail SMTP
        Email-->>API: Email sent
        API-->>Client: { ok: true }
    end

    Note over Client,DB: Tracking Flow
    Client->>API: POST /api/track<br/>{type: "pageview", path}
    API->>API: Extract request metadata<br/>(IP, User-Agent, etc.)
    API->>DB: Create PageView record
    DB-->>API: Success
    API-->>Client: { success: true }

    Note over Client,DB: RSS Feed Flow
    Client->>API: GET /rss.xml
    API->>DB: Query published posts<br/>(limit 50, ordered by date)
    DB-->>API: Posts data
    API->>API: Generate RSS XML
    API-->>Client: RSS XML (200 OK)

    Note over Client,Cookie: Logout Flow
    Client->>API: GET /admin/logout
    API->>Cookie: Clear admin cookie
    Cookie-->>API: Cookie cleared
    API-->>Client: 302 Redirect to /






